<p><strong>Core beliefs.</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Philosophy – These are your highest-order beliefs that guide all others.</li>
  <li>Personal Productivity – The keys for you to function well.</li>
  <li>Work – How to succeed in your career.</li>
  <li>People – Who to surround yourself with and how to connect with them.</li>
  <li>Relationships – How to be a partner, friend and parent.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Common topics.</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Physical health – What keeps you physically healthy and how do you balance that with the demands of life.</li>
  <li>Mental health – How to find balance, stability, satisfaction and maybe even happiness.</li>
  <li>Money – How to get it, what to do with it, and how to feel about it.</li>
  <li>Possessions – Which possessions are worth having, why and how do you use them?</li>
  <li>Politics and policies – How do you land on specific political questions.</li>
  <li>Traps to avoid – Common beliefs or situations that can and should be avoided.</li>
  <li>Mysteries of the universe – Are their aliens? Are we in a simulation?</li>
  <li>Influences – Articles, talks, videos, movies and music that move or inform you.</li>
</ul>

